    "like_dislike_summary": {
      "pos_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "The college lecture schedule is very durable you can leave the class whenever you want.",
          "name": "Siddharth Sandesh Raaje",
          "course_tag_name": "BA"
        },
        {
          "text": "The college teachers are very friendly with the students.",
          "name": "Siddharth Sandesh Raaje",
          "course_tag_name": "BA"
        },
        {
          "text": "The thing which i liked about this college is mostly its fees which is very affordable.",
          "name": "Siddharth Sandesh Raaje",
          "course_tag_name": "BA"
        },
        {
          "text": "Overall everything is good but not best from my perspective",
          "name": "Abhishek patil",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "The teachers are also good and teach best of what they are capable, Im from science department so I don’t know about the rest.",
          "name": "Abhishek patil",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "The environment inside the college is very clean and neat, strictness is also good so that students do not misbehave, functions and sports events are carried out every year which I like personally.",
          "name": "Abhishek patil",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "The college teachers are very helpful and informative in any case of study problems or any career related issues.",
          "name": "Rajat Jitendra Biramane",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "Mumbai University has very good online services to take admissions into our interested field.",
          "name": "Rajat Jitendra Biramane",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "The college interior is good and they are still trying theri best to develop their innterior.",
          "name": "Yash Vikram Mhatre",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "The teachers that they teaches are of very good quality, they help us to unterstand everything if we have some doubt in it.",
          "name": "Yash Vikram Mhatre",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        }
      ],
      "neg_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "Many teachers might be friendly but however some of them are extremely aggressive.",
          "name": "Siddharth Sandesh Raaje",
          "course_tag_name": "BA"
        },
        {
          "text": "The college admission staff is the worst staff I've ever seen.",
          "name": "Siddharth Sandesh Raaje",
          "course_tag_name": "BA"
        },
        {
          "text": "The people sitting in the office for official purposes do not talk and act nicely and they are rude",
          "name": "Abhishek patil",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "The sports department of this college only supports the softball game and didn’t pay attention to the other games such as volleyball, carom, shot put, etc",
          "name": "Abhishek patil",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "The exam committee of this college is worst and they didn’t co operate with the students neatly and act rudely as they are paying our fees",
          "name": "Abhishek patil",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "There is no specific well maintained canteen of the college",
          "name": "Rajat Jitendra Biramane",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "No parking space alloted for the degree students as they all parked on the road so the traffic issue infront of the college",
          "name": "Rajat Jitendra Biramane",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "The college toilet is not good the college toilet property is break.",
          "name": "Yash Vikram Mhatre",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "There is no college ground beacuse the students are unable to do outside activities like playing outdoor games.",
          "name": "Yash Vikram Mhatre",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "The college office staff are not much cooperative with the students.",
          "name": "Yash Vikram Mhatre",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        }
      ]
